{
  "//": [
    "TypeScript strict mode incremental — caminho documentado em CLAUDE.md §10.",
    "Este config liga strict flags (noImplicitAny, strictNullChecks etc) APENAS pra",
    "files explicitamente listados em `include` abaixo. Outros files continuam com",
    "tsconfig.app.json (strict: false).",
    "",
    "Adicione files novos / migrados aqui conforme forem ficando strict-clean.",
    "Roda via `bun run typecheck:strict`. Quando 100% do src estiver listado, mover",
    "os flags pra tsconfig.app.json e deletar este arquivo."
  ],
  "extends": "./tsconfig.app.json",
  "compilerOptions": {
    "noImplicitAny": true,
    "strictNullChecks": true,
    "strict": true,
    "noFallthroughCasesInSwitch": true,
    "noUnusedLocals": true,
    "noUnusedParameters": true
  },
  "include": [
    "src/vite-env.d.ts",
    "src/lib/logger.ts",
    "src/lib/format.ts",
    "src/lib/phone.ts",
    "src/lib/agruparPorMes.ts",
    "src/lib/help-utils.ts",
    "src/hooks/useNetworkStatus.ts",
    "src/hooks/useInfiniteScroll.ts",
    "src/hooks/useBarcodeDetector.ts",
    "src/hooks/useFarmerPerformance.ts",
    "src/hooks/useFarmerExperiments.ts",
    "src/hooks/useTacticalPlan.ts",
    "src/hooks/useCrossSellEngine.ts",
    "src/hooks/useBundleEngine.ts",
    "src/hooks/useFinanceiro.ts",
    "src/hooks/useCopilotEngine.ts",
    "src/hooks/useFarmerGovernance.ts",
    "src/hooks/useFarmerScoring.ts",
    "src/pages/FarmerCopilot.tsx",
    "src/pages/FinanceiroConciliacao.tsx",
    "src/components/financeiro/CockpitDrillDown.tsx",
    "src/pages/FinanceiroCockpit.tsx",
    "src/pages/AdminReposicaoAplicacao.tsx"
  ]
}
